## Closable Notes

To allow users to dismiss the note, set the <MdxBadge>closable</MdxBadge> prop to <MdxBadge>true</MdxBadge>.

<ComponentPreview name="note-demo" variant="closable" />

## Usage

<div className="not-prose space-y-4">
  <p className="text-base">First, you have to import <MdxBadge>Note.tsx</MdxBadge> in your file:</p>

  <Pre className="language-typescript">
    {`import { Note } from "@/components/Note"`}
  </Pre>

  <p className="text-base">Then, you can use the <MdxBadge>Note</MdxBadge> component in your file:</p>

  <Pre className="language-jsx">
    {`const MyComponent = () => {
      return (
        <div>
          <Note variant="info" closable>  
              Turbopack is a high-performance bundler and dev server for Next.js. Enabling this option ensures faster builds and an improved development experience.  
          </Note>  
        </div>
        );
      };`}
  </Pre>
</div>
